title: Serena Williams shows off `butt` in skimpy bright orange swimsuit
text: Serena Williams shows off `butt` in skimpy bright orange swimsuit Monday, 12 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) *London, Oct.6 (ANI): Serena Williams recently showed off her butt and curves in a skimpy bright orange swimsuit, while hanging out with her pals in San Marcos, Texas.* London, Oct.6 (ANI): Serena Williams recently showed off her butt and curves in a skimpy bright orange swimsuit, while hanging out with her pals in San Marcos, Texas. The 34-year-old tennis player, who enjoyed her weekend with her pal Colton Haynes and another gal-pal, flashed her bottom at the camera as she held onto her red rubber ring, while the 'Arrow' actor flaunted his muscles as he posed for the pic, The Mirror reports. Serena, who is rumored to be dating rapper Drake took to her Instagram page to share the pic which shows her and her two other pals and wrote, "Core memories with @valgabond @coltonhaynes love you guys." In addition to this, the tennis player's gal-pal posted another snapshot of the trio taking a dip in the river alongside caption, "Adventures and belly laughs all weekend long. Love these guys #corememories."(ANI)
